      <title>执政党非洲人国民大会 (ANC) 探索联合执政选项，兰特看跌押注增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/zar-bearish-bets-rise-as-anc-top-brass-discuss-coalition-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在非洲人国民大会领导层着手解决紧迫的联盟建设问题之际，交易员们押注兰特将进一步下跌，此前选举结果与几十年的先例相悖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/zar-bearish-bets-rise-as-anc-top-brass-discuss-coalition-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:48:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
